Package: dmdr
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Mode Decomposition
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Julia", "Worthington",
      email = "julia.worthington@colorado.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package computes the dynamic mode decomposition (DMD)
    of data and plots the resulting modes, underlying dynamics, and eigenvalues.
    It also approximates the original data using the DMD.
